Package pl.prawko.prawko_server.model

Class Answer

java.lang.Object
pl.prawko.prawko_server.model.Answer
@Entity public class Answer extends Object
Represents a Answer entity within application.

A Answer has:

  • id - generated unique identifier
  • correct - indicates if this answer is correct

Relationships:

  • Question: Multiple answers belong to single question
  • AnswerTranslation: An answer can have multiple translations
  • Exam: An answer can be associated with multiple exams
The entity is mapped do the database table answer. All setters are returning Answer itself enabling method chaining.
